data.title: The new angels of Victoria’s Secret
data.meta_description: A very expected event, the collections of the lingerie brand Victoria’s Secret. And why ? For the outfits of course, the fashion shows on stage and the dream creatures which highlight the few centimeters necessary to each creation. Presentation of
data.text:
The official presentation of this new cosmopolitan team of models with perfect measurements took place on 29 July in Times Square ! It was in the heart of New York that the new recruits could show their pretty face. Who are they where do they come from ? Kate Grigorieva 25 years old Russia, Taylor Hill 19 years old US, Elsa Hosk 26 years old Suede, Martha Hunt 26 years old US, Jac Jagaciak 21 years old Poland, Stella Maxwell 24 years old Belgium, Lais Ribeiro 24 years old Brazil, Sara Sampaio 24 years old Portugal, Romee Strijd 20 years old Neverlands et Jasmine Tookes 24 years old US.

They are unknown for the moment but being part of the team of Victoria’s Angels is acts as a springboard for the career of a model.

Wearing a simple white jean and a tee shirt , the ten young women were presented to walk on the pink carpet. Organized each summer at the same period, this event enable the muses to present the new range of the brand, plainly baptized “body” this year.
